      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SELECT CASH (1) turned in a solid run last start over 435m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (24.93). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Can atone. HOT ROCKER (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Brindle Chic (25.06) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. SOMERTON ANN (5) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (26.80) last time in a Grade 5 at Warragul. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. The form from her last run stacks up well. Worth following up. SMOOTH TIGER (8) is not to be discarded.",
